        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "text": "- Lester's Relationship with his Father (Trauma + Exile), watch other curated interviews such as the interviews with: Amaury Pérez, Yadira Otero, or Marco en Marcos. "
